    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[fear, mind-affecting];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Cleric 6, Sorcerer 6, Wizard 6;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (mercury and phosphorus, plus powdered diamond and opal with a total value of at least 1,000 gp)<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;10 minutes<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;0 feet<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Effect:</strong>&nbsp;One symbol<br>\n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;See Text<br>\n    <strong>Power Points/Spell Points Cost:</strong>&nbsp;11<br>\n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;Will Negates\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\nThis spell functions like <i>symbol of death</i>, except that all creatures within 60 feet of the <i>symbol of fear </i>instead become panicked for 1 round per caster level.\n</p><p><i>Note: </i>Magic traps such as <i>symbol of fear </i>are hard to detect and disable. A rogue (only) can use the Search skill to find a <i>symbol of fear </i>and Disable Device to thwart it. The DC in each case is 25 + spell level, or 31 for <i>symbol of fear</i>.\n</p><p><i>Material Component: </i>Mercury and phosphorus, plus powdered diamond and opal with a total value of at least 1,000 gp.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
